text: Crystal Lowe (born January 20, 1981) is a Canadian actress and model. She is best known for her roles in horror movies such as roles as Children of the Corn: Revelation (2001), Final Destination 3 (2006), Black Christmas (2006) and Wrong Turn 2: Dead End (2007). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian models Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Canadian television actors Category:Canadian voice actors Category:Canadian child actors Category:Canadian stage actors Category:Actors from Vancouver
